WEBVTT

00:01.870 --> 00:04.750
GIORGIO A. TSOUKALOS:
This wall exists here,

00:04.750 --> 00:08.670
at one of the most
inaccessible places.

00:08.670 --> 00:13.680
These types of walls,
they exist all over the world.

00:13.680 --> 00:18.640
The building style is not
similar, it is identical.

00:18.640 --> 00:21.390
NARRATOR: Were alien structures
built on Earth

00:21.390 --> 00:24.270
as part of a master plan?

00:24.270 --> 00:26.980
FREDDY SILVA: That these temples
actually act as batteries.

00:26.980 --> 00:30.320
They store energy and they also
allow the energy to expand

00:30.320 --> 00:32.320
at certain times during the day.

00:32.320 --> 00:36.410
NARRATOR: Could they reveal
an extraterrestrial connection?

00:36.410 --> 00:38.910
RICHARD CASSARO: Ancient
cultures around the world

00:38.910 --> 00:41.700
connected their temples
to each other

00:41.700 --> 00:43.790
almost like
a master circuit board.

00:43.790 --> 00:47.380
NARRATOR: And did they serve
a larger purpose,

00:47.380 --> 00:50.250
one that reaches beyond Earth?

00:50.250 --> 00:53.470
DAVID CHILDRESS: They're somehow
looking at the Earth from space

00:53.470 --> 00:58.140
and seeing how these structures
would fit around the globe.

00:58.140 --> 01:02.430
Who could be doing this,
except for extraterrestrials?

01:02.430 --> 01:04.390
